@Deco\_y  

I assume you mean [Gideon's Lawkeeper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gideon's Lawkeeper) rather than [Gideon's Avenger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gideon's Avenger); if so, you would be quite right (all 3 cards together would be a nice combo as well). Also, the [Crown of Empires](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crown of Empires) would work as well for a mono black deck (although at a higher price). Basically anything that can allow you to tap your opponent's creatures is awesome with this guy (especially to kill those annoying ones with Vigilance).   

Definitely one of my favourite cards.
